<li>Period: period 4</li>
<li>Element category: alkali metal</li>
<li>Electron configuration: 4s1</li>
<li>Per shell: 2, 8, 8, 1</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Physical properties</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Phase: gas</li>
